This project includes original work by brAinphreAk:
- Pager hardware integration (pagerctl.py, display system, menu system)
- MIPS cross-compiled binaries (sfreerdp, smb2-cat, smb2-find, smb2-share-enum, xfreerdp)
- MIPS shared libraries (libsodium, nmap, smb, bcrypt, cffi, cryptography, etc.)
- Device classifier, vulnerability scanner enhancements, theme/skin engine
- Web UI and all pager-specific adaptations

